{
  "texts": [
    "We now turn to the category of country of publication of the journals (Figure 7).",
    "It was found that, according to the location of the journals, the United Kingdom is the country, where the largest number of articles on the subject have been published (85).",
    "This is followed by the United States, where 45 articles have been published on the subject.",
    "It is followed by Spain, with the publication of 20 articles.",
    "Smaller figures can be seen in Switzerland (seven), Brazil (six), India (six), the Netherlands (six), and Portugal (six)."
  ]
}